fosters.name: Toothless
fosters.description: Toothless is an instant purr machine and very affectionate. He likes to cuddle and while doing so you can admire his beautiful face! It's not required, but if looking for 2 kittens, Toothless would like to be adopted with Light Fury!
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: Light Fury
fosters.description: When Light Fury first arrived to her foster's home, she was very shy and hissy. Now, she loves to explore her foster parent's home and has overcome her fear of humans. She gets along with the other kittens in the home but loves to be independent.
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: Meatlug
fosters.description: Meatlug is curious but still seems a little reluctant to join group activites. Luckily, Meatlug is still young and impressionable so there is much optimism that her personality will change over time.
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: Stormfly
fosters.description: Stormfly is a social butterfly with the humans and really likes sitting in laps. He loves to interact with visitors and is engaged with his surroundings. Stormfly likes to give and receive love so will really make a wonderful companion!

fosters.name: Hookfang
fosters.description: Hookfang really loves Temptations treats so that is a great way to win him over. He also likes to play with wand toys and anything that jingles or he can chase.

fosters.name: Leonardo
fosters.description: Leonardo is very energetic and loves to chase wand toys. He also loves to climb and you can usually find him at the highest point of any cat tree! Leonardo enjoys being petted all over and will seek you out for affection.
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: Donatello
fosters.description: Donatello is very active and loves to run and jump. He is also good at puzzle type toys that require some kitty smarts to figure out. He really likes having his ears scratched and he loves snuggling with humans
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: Raphael
fosters.description: Raphael is a little hissy meeting new kittens but fun eventually takes over and he ends up playing with them. He enjoys back scratches and belly rubs so much that he will go looking for attention to get them.
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: Michelangelo
fosters.description: Donatello is a little bit shy but enjoys being petted once he checks you out. He likes the company of other kittens and can be a bit chatty if you leave him alone without a friend. He will do great in a multi-pet home!
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: Shredder
fosters.description: Shredder is an independent cat. She doesn't seem to mind other cats, but also hasn't actively sought out a cat friend yet. She likes to chill in a cozy bed observing the scene and is receptive to slow petting.

fosters.name: (Sailor) Moon
fosters.description: Moon is by far the most “chill” kitten out of his litter. He is VERY comfortable around the 2 dogs that he gets to spend time with currently and loves to snuggle with his foster parent at bed time. Moon is looking forward to finding his forever home!
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: (Sailor) Venus
fosters.description: Venus is curious about everything! She was the first in her litter to figure out how to do things. She doesn't play as much as her siblings & feels more comfortable being independent.
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: (Sailor) Mars
fosters.description: Mars was shy when arriving to his foster home but now that he's comfortable he loves to explore his surroundings. He doesn't like being picked up or held on his back but will otherwise enjoy belly scratching when just laying around.
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: (Sailor) Mercury
fosters.description: Mercury is the smallest in his litter so sometimes he acts a little insecure. He enjoys being petted but not being held. He also loves to snuggle with his siblings on a cozy blanket.
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help schedule that appointment.

fosters.name: (Sailor) Jupiter
fosters.description: Jupiter is a very sweet girl that love pets and purrs up a storm. Did you notice that she has 2 different colored eyes?
fosters.spayedNeutered: No, but we can help make that appointment.

adoptedFosters.name: Wednesday
adoptedFosters.description: Wednesday is now living her best life with Sirius Black!

adoptedFosters.name: Friday
adoptedFosters.description: Friday is now living his best life with Draco Malfoy!

messages.name: Sirius Black
messages.subject: Donate
messages.body: I have extra litter I no longer need. Would you guys be able to use it?
